OL,6,FWatch the moment Christine Rawle is
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of murdering her
OL,8,Fhusband
OL,10,FThis is the moment a woman accused of
OL,11,Fstabbing her husband to death was
OL,12,Farrested for murder.
OL,14,FChristine Rawle, 70, at their north
OL,15,FDevon home in 2022.
OL,17,FJurors at Exeter Crown Court have been
OL,18,Fshown video footage of Mrs Rawle being
OL,19,Fplaced in handcuffs and into the back
OL,20,Fof a police van.
