OL,6,FShe asked officers: "How can you love
OL,7,Fsomeone and do everything for someone
OL,8,Fwho is so calculatingly nasty to you?"
OL,10,F"He is narcissistic. It seems like a
OL,11,Fbad dream. I just wish it was me, I
OL,12,Fwish he had killed me.
OL,14,F"He just pushed me and pushed me and
OL,15,Fpushed me. He tortures me. I tried to
OL,16,Fget away many times. I wanted a
OL,17,Fdivorce."
