OL,6,FShe added: "He's not going to hurt me
OL,7,Fanymore. I want to wake up. I want to
OL,8,Fwake up from this."
OL,10,FMrs Rawle also claimed that she tried
OL,11,Fto call the police to report her
OL,12,Fhusband's behaviour but that it took a
OL,13,Fvery long time to get through.
OL,15,FJurors have also been shown a series
OL,16,Fof nine video clips made by the
OL,17,Fdefendant on her mobile phone weeks
OL,18,Fbefore her husband's death.
