OL,6,F"I've asked you not to speak to me,"
OL,7,Fshe says in the video. "I am not
OL,8,Finterested in what you've got to say.
OL,9,FShut up and leave me alone or I will
OL,10,Fcall the police."
OL,12,FMr Rawle tells his wife she is
OL,13,F"p***ing (her) life away".
OL,15,F"Who puts the fuel in the car, who
OL,16,Fprovides the car?" he says.
OL,18,FLater he adds: "You're only ill when
OL,19,Fyou're with me."
OL,21,Fand the trial continues.
